{"tid":1540374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你以為林鄭真係想撤回？少年人你太年輕了","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:11:45.000Z","uid":84123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a537d25c6f52d02061e818cc3505399698ed41","tid":1540374,"uid":84123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:22:03.000Z","msg":"林鄭今日放一輪風話有機會撤回<br />\n等外國新聞報林鄭撤回<br />\n先至播片講「動議撤回」<br />\n司馬遷之心路人皆見<br />\n<br />\n明顯地佢話撤回其實<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係同你講</span><br />\n係同外國講香港搞掂左<br />\n唔再係送中<br />\n減低中美貿易戰美國對中國施壓<br />\n令外國投資者恢復信心<br />\n同時佢都係向和理非講<br />\n「我撤回你好收貨，等我拉鳩班勇武，你地可以開心喇！」<br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n今日林鄭係想<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">將外國壓力同和理非抽走</span></span><br />\n搞散呢場運動呢場革命<br />\n我地要向和理非同外國做文宣<br />\n話比佢地知仲未完<br />\n<br />\n最後十六字真言<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"48d45b97a4468838d6af9e18d0ac5b063cfe620d","tid":1540374,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0faf68483c9cdce2e5a506456f1a656543a1c9","tid":1540374,"uid":84123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:24:43.000Z","msg":"大家唔好收貨<br />\n唔好放棄"},{"pid":"5f4911f35c4824da597ee257560e1eae08b45085","tid":1540374,"uid":84123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:40:46.000Z","msg":"怒推<br />\n怒洗版"},{"pid":"8af421a71758965f391b054b2dc339f460fea384","tid":1540374,"uid":287383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:43:03.000Z","msg":"emmm是司馬昭。。。"},{"pid":"bb5661f642051008fda3ea756955f97839d76bea","tid":1540374,"uid":84123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8af421a71758965f391b054b2dc339f460fea384","tid":1540374,"uid":287383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:43:03.0